				<wikidot:authorName>Agent MacLeod</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1922529</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Its species banned it because it is different. It has stated that it has abilities that the rest of its species does not&#8230; This thing is a skip amongst skips. It's a standard Mary-Sue reality bender, just one that got banned by its species' equivalent to the GOC or Foundation. Hence, the unreliable narration and the crush on the researcher. How has no one noticed this before?</p> <p>Edit: Also, I'm adding this to my list of &quot;Skips I wouldn't mind hugging.&quot;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
